import React from "react";
import {Box, Typography, styled, Button, Stack} from "@mui/material"
import Background from "./../Images/HeroBackground.jpg";

const RightBox = styled(Box)({
    backgroundImage:`url(${Background})`, 
    backgroundAttachment: "fixed",
    backgroundSize: "60vh",
    
});

const Header = styled(Stack)({
    background: "#BFD200",
    textAlign: "left",
});

//StyledBox als Parent von LeftBox und RIghtBox?
export default function Hero() {
    return (
        <Box bgcolor="black">
            <Stack direction="column">
                <Header direction="row">
                    <Box flex={1}></Box>
                    <Stack direction="row" alignItems="center" flex={2}>
                        <Typography variant="h4">
                            DEIN DIGITALER 
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{fontWeight:"bold", p:"5px"}}>
                            CO-TRAINER
                        </Typography>
                    </Stack>
                </Header>
                <Stack direction="row">
                    <Box flex={1}></Box>
                    <RightBox flex={2}>
                                <Typography>
                                    COACHING MADE EASY
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    MINIMALER AUFWAND.
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    MAXIMALER ERFOLG.
                                </Typography>
                                <Typography>
                                    Weil der Trainerjob Spa√ü machen soll!
                                </Typography>
                                <Button>
                                    LOS GEHT'S
                                </Button>
                            <Stack direction="row">
                                <Stack direction="column">
                                    <Typography>
                                        6.000+
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Typography>
                                        Trainer
                                    </Typography>
                                </Stack>
                                <Stack direction="column">
                                    <Typography>
                                        5 Mio
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Typography>
                                        Trainings
                                    </Typography>
                                </Stack>
                                <Stack direction="column">
                                    <Typography>
                                        3.000+
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Typography>
                                        Spiele
                                    </Typography>
                                </Stack>
                            </Stack>
                    </RightBox>
                </Stack>
            </Stack>
 
        </Box>
    )
}
